urls.title: How to prebook add ons?
urls.description: You can prebook add ons such as seat selection, meal, and checked baggage allowance at the “Add-ons” page. You will be landed on the page shown below after selecting your flight destination(s), date, and time. If you did not prebook any add ons when making a flight booking, you can purchase your add ons after your booking is confirmed via My Bookings, AirAsia Mobile Apps or AVA before the cut-off time. Click on “My Bookings” on airasia.com. Enter your booking number, family name/surname and departure
